"rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11828,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/iman-leave-sins-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":34525,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Conscience: Leave sins that shake your soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: A man asked the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhat is faith?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf you are happy with your good deeds and saddened by your bad deeds, you are a believer.\u201d The man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is sin?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35811,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/27\/iman-shuhh-combined\/","url_meta":{"origin":34525,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Greed: Faith and miserliness never combined in heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe dust in the way of Allah and the smoke of Hell can never be combined on the face of a man. Greed and faith can never be combined in the heart.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3111\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuami